title: AMERICAN GODS Season 2 Episode 7 Breakdown & Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: Sorry for the late upload on this one guys! My season finale breakdown should be up sometime on Sunday!
I'm kind of pissed they killed the best character.
Mad Sweeney was one of the best characters :( gonna miss him
I love how they showed him teleporting the spear into the Hoard a place that Wednesday can't access! :D

He didn't abandon people on the battlefield, he was cursed before the battle began and lost his mind during the battle which caused him to leave the battlefield. He stayed in the woods because he began to lose his mind and his memories.
